headline: Tesla earnings, fresh Fed commentary: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Wednesday, October 22, including corporate earnings results from companies like Tesla (TSLA), AT&T (T), and IBM (IBM), as well as economic commentary from Federal Reserve governor Michael Barr. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.

headline: Inflation Data; Intel and Tesla Earnings: What to Watch This Week
summary: The U.S. government shutdown continues, but investors won't be completely starved for economic data. Friday brings a delayed look at September’s consumer-price index, a key inflation reading that will factor into the Federal Reserve’s next decision on interest rates.
